      <title>[筆記] 建立一個帶著走的 VIM 環境 Creating portable Vim environment</title>
      <link>https://hu.mc4.us/p/%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98-%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%B8%B6%E8%91%97%E8%B5%B0%E7%9A%84-vim-%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-creating-portable-vim-environment/</link>
